
## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Kali Linux (or any Linux with Splunk)
- 8GB+ RAM
- Root/sudo access
- Optional: Ubuntu VM for remote attack simulation

### One-Line Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/soc-detection-lab.git
cd soc-detection-lab
chmod +x scripts/setup.sh
sudo ./scripts/setup.sh
